name: MasterDude
0:
”Alexa, ask Master Dude news from India”
”Alexa, ask Master Dude what is happening in Hollywood”
”Alexa, ask Master Dude horoscope for Gemini”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: master dude
des: Master Dude's purpose is to give more news than a flash briefing would give. Users can ask Master Dude to provide news in specific categories like Business, World, Sports, Entertainment (Hollywood and Bollywood), etc. from USA and India. Master Dude can also tell you today's horoscope for any sun sign or even current weather of a city. Master Dude can also dictate a math table of any number.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
